article.description: — Tyrone Lyons had 21 points as Southern defeated Southeastern Louisiana 72-66 on Saturday.
article.headline: Lyons scores 21 to lead Southern over SE Louisiana 72-66
article.linkText: Lyons scores 21 to lead Southern over SE Louisiana 72-66
article.story: BATON ROUGE, La. -- — Tyrone Lyons had 21 points as Southern defeated Southeastern Louisiana 72-66 on Saturday. Brion Whitley had 11 points for Southern (5-6). Keon Clergeot had 16 points for the Lions (4-6). Jalyn Hinton added 14 points and seven rebounds. Joe Kasperzyk had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
